en-us: If 'actionName' key contains a bound action, removes function from being called by all input that it was bound by (if function was also bound by a different action name as well, those bound input are still active). Will also remove any touch button created (if button was manipulated manually there is no guarantee it will be cleaned up).
zh-cn: 若 'actionName' 键包含绑定操作，阻止函数被其绑定的所有输入调用 (若函数还被其他操作名称绑定，则这些绑定的输入仍然有效)。还会移除创建的触碰按钮 (如果按钮被人工操作过，则无法保证它一定会被清除)。

Source: Removes all functions bound. No actionNames will remain. All touch buttons will be removed. If button was manipulated manually there is no guarantee it will be cleaned up.
en-us: Removes all functions bound. No actionNames will remain. All touch buttons will be removed. If button was manipulated manually there is no guarantee it will be cleaned up.
zh-cn: 移除所有绑定的函数。不保留任何 actionName。将会移除所有触碰按钮。如果按钮被人工操作过，则无法保证它一定会被清除。

Source: Returns a table with info regarding the function bound with 'actionName'. Table has the keys 'title' (current title that was set with SetTitle) 'image' (image set with SetImage) 'description' (description set with SetDescription) 'inputTypes' (tuple containing all input bound for this 'actionName') 'createTouchButton' (whether or not we created a touch button for this 'actionName').
en-us: Returns a table with info regarding the function bound with 'actionName'. Table has the keys 'title' (current title that was set with SetTitle) 'image' (image set with SetImage) 'description' (description set with SetDescription) 'inputTypes' (tuple containing all input bound for this 'actionName') 'createTouchButton' (whether or not we created a touch button for this 'actionName').
zh-cn: 返回一个包含与 'actionName' 绑定的函数的信息的格。表键包括 'title' (通过 SetTitle 设置的当前标题)、'image' (通过 SetImage 设置的图像)、'description' (通过 SetDescription 设置的描述)、'inputTypes' (包含此 'actionName' 绑定的所有输入的元组)、'createTouchButton' (我们是否为此 actionName' 创建触碰按钮)。

Source: Returns a table with all bound action info. Each entry is a key with 'actionName' and value being the same table you would get from ContextActionService:GetBoundActionInfo('actionName').
en-us: Returns a table with all bound action info. Each entry is a key with 'actionName' and value being the same table you would get from ContextActionService:GetBoundActionInfo('actionName').
zh-cn: 返回一个包含所有绑定操作信息的表。表的每个条目都是一个拥有 'actionName' 的键且取值与你通过 ContextActionService:GetBoundActioninfo('actionName') 所获得的表相同。

Source: If 'actionName' key contains a bound action, then this will return the touch button (if was created). Returns nil if a touch button was not created. No guarantees are made whether button will be retrievable when button is manipulated.
en-us: If 'actionName' key contains a bound action, then this will return the touch button (if was created). Returns nil if a touch button was not created. No guarantees are made whether button will be retrievable when button is manipulated.
zh-cn: 若 'actionName' 包含绑定操作，将返回触碰按键 (如果已创建)。如果未创建触碰按钮则返回空值。若按钮被操作，无法保证是否能检索到按钮。

Source: A service used to query and award points for Roblox users using the universal point system.
en-us: A service used to query and award points for Roblox users using the universal point system.
zh-cn: 用于为使用通用积分系统的 Roblox 用户进行查询和奖励积分的服务。

Source: Fired when points are successfully awarded 'userId'. Also returns the updated balance of points for usedId in universe via 'userBalanceInUniverse', total points via 'userTotalBalance', and the amount points that were awarded via 'pointsAwarded'. This event fires on the server and also all clients in the game that awarded the points.
en-us: Fired when points are successfully awarded 'userId'. Also returns the updated balance of points for usedId in universe via 'userBalanceInUniverse', total points via 'userTotalBalance', and the amount points that were awarded via 'pointsAwarded'. This event fires on the server and also all clients in the game that awarded the points.
zh-cn: 积分成功奖励给 'userId' 时触发。还会通过 'userBalanceInUniverse' 返回此宇宙中 usedId 更新后的积分余额，通过 'userTotalBalance' 返回总积分，以及通过 'pointsAwarded' 返回奖励的积分。此事件同时在服务器及所有获得奖励积分的客户端触发。

Source: Will attempt to award the 'amount' points to 'userId', returns 'userId' awarded to, the number of points awarded, the new point total the user has in the game, and the total number of points the user now has. Will also fire PointsService.PointsAwarded. Works with server scripts ONLY.
en-us: Will attempt to award the 'amount' points to 'userId', returns 'userId' awarded to, the number of points awarded, the new point total the user has in the game, and the total number of points the user now has. Will also fire PointsService.PointsAwarded. Works with server scripts ONLY.
zh-cn: 会尝试奖励 'amount' 点积分给 'userId'，返回接受奖励的 'userId'、奖励的积分数量以及用户在游戏中的新积分总数。还会触发 PointsService.PointsAwarded。仅适用于服务器脚本。

Source: Returns the overall balance of points that player with userId has (the sum of all points across all games). Works with server scripts ONLY.
en-us: Returns the overall balance of points that player with userId has (the sum of all points across all games). Works with server scripts ONLY.
zh-cn: 返回该 userId 的玩家的整体积分余额 (所有游戏的全部积分总额)。仅适用于服务器脚本。

Source: Returns the balance of points that player with userId has in the current game (all placeID points combined within the game). Works with server scripts ONLY.
en-us: Returns the balance of points that player with userId has in the current game (all placeID points combined within the game). Works with server scripts ONLY.
zh-cn: 返回该 userId 的玩家爱当前游戏中的积分余额 (游戏中所有 placeID 的积分总和)。仅适用于服务器脚本。

Source: Returns the number of points the current universe can award to players. Works with server scripts ONLY.
en-us: Returns the number of points the current universe can award to players. Works with server scripts ONLY.
zh-cn: 返回当前宇宙可以奖励给玩家的积分数量。仅适用于服务器脚本。

Source: A database of strings used in the game and their translations.
en-us: A database of strings used in the game and their translations.
zh-cn: 在游戏及翻译中使用的字符串数据库。

Source: Gets the system's preferred language (A Language enum).
en-us: Gets the system's preferred language (A Language enum).
zh-cn: 获取系统的首选语言 (语言枚举)。

Source: Gets the system's LocaleId (Ex: "en-US").
en-us: Gets the system's LocaleId (Ex: "en-US").
zh-cn: 获取系统的 LocaleId (例如: "en-US")。

Source: Will prompt 'player' to purchase the item associated with 'assetId'.  'equipIfPurchased' is an optional argument that will give the item to the player immediately if they buy it (only applies to gear).  'currencyType' is also optional and will attempt to prompt the user with a specified currency if the product can be purchased with this currency, otherwise we use the default currency of the product.
en-us: Will prompt 'player' to purchase the item associated with 'assetId'.  'equipIfPurchased' is an optional argument that will give the item to the player immediately if they buy it (only applies to gear).  'currencyType' is also optional and will attempt to prompt the user with a specified currency if the product can be purchased with this currency, otherwise we use the default currency of the product.
zh-cn: 将提示 'player' 购买与 'assetId' 相关联的物品。'equipIfPurchased' 为可选参数，将在玩家购买物品后立即将其给予玩家 (仅限装备)。'currencyType' 也是可选参数，若产品可以通过指定货币进行购买，则会尝试提示用户使用该货币，否则我们会使用产品的默认货币。

Source: Takes one argument "assetId" which should be a number of an asset on www.roblox.com.  Returns a table containing the product information (if this process fails, returns an empty table).
en-us: Takes one argument "assetId" which should be a number of an asset on www.roblox.com.  Returns a table containing the product information (if this process fails, returns an empty table).
zh-cn: 需指定一个参数 “assetId”，该参数应为 www.roblox.com 上某个资源的编号。返回一个包含产品信息的表（若此过程失败，则返回空表）。

Source: Checks to see if 'Player' owns the product associated with 'assetId'. Returns true if the player owns it, false otherwise. This call will produce a warning if called on a guest player.
en-us: Checks to see if 'Player' owns the product associated with 'assetId'. Returns true if the player owns it, false otherwise. This call will produce a warning if called on a guest player.
zh-cn: 检查 'Player' 是否拥有与 'assetId' 相关的产品。若玩家拥有则返回 true，否则返回 false。若对访客玩家调用，还会生成一条警告信息。

Source:
Callback that is executed for pending Developer Product receipts.

If this function does not return Enum.ProductPurchaseDecision.PurchaseGranted, then you will not be granted the money for the purchase!

The callback will be invoked with a table, containing the following informational fields:

  • PlayerId: int64 - the id of the player making the purchase.
  • PlaceIdWherePurchased: int64: - the specific place where the purchase was made.
  • PurchaseId: string - a unique identifier for the purchase, should be used to prevent granting an item multiple times for one purchase.
  • ProductId: int64 - the id of the purchased product.
  • CurrencyType: CurrencyType - the type of currency used (Tix, Robux).
  • CurrencySpent: int - the amount of currency spent on the product for this purchase.
en-us:
Callback that is executed for pending Developer Product receipts.

If this function does not return Enum.ProductPurchaseDecision.PurchaseGranted, then you will not be granted the money for the purchase!

The callback will be invoked with a table, containing the following informational fields:

  • PlayerId: int64 - the id of the player making the purchase.
  • PlaceIdWherePurchased: int64: - the specific place where the purchase was made.
  • PurchaseId: string - a unique identifier for the purchase, should be used to prevent granting an item multiple times for one purchase.
  • ProductId: int64 - the id of the purchased product.
  • CurrencyType: CurrencyType - the type of currency used (Tix, Robux).
  • CurrencySpent: int - the amount of currency spent on the product for this purchase.
zh-cn:
对待处理的开发者产品收据执行的回调。

若此函数未返回 Enum.ProductPurchaseDecision.PurchaseGranted，你将无法获得购买所支付的金钱!

将使用包含以下信息字段的表调用回调:

  • PlayerId: int64 - 进行购买的玩家的身份标识。
  • PlaceIdWherePurchased: int64 - 进行购买的具体位置。
  • PurchaseId: string - 该次购买的唯一识别码，可用于防止一次购买多次授予物品。
  • ProductId: int64 - 被购买产品的标识。
  • CurrencyType: CurrencyType - 使用的货币类型 (Tix、Robux)。
  • CurrencySpent: int - 本次购买中花费的货币数量。

Source: Fired when a 'player' dismisses a purchase dialog for 'assetId'.  If the player purchased the item 'isPurchased' will be true, otherwise it will be false. This call will produce a warning if called on a guest player.
en-us: Fired when a 'player' dismisses a purchase dialog for 'assetId'.  If the player purchased the item 'isPurchased' will be true, otherwise it will be false. This call will produce a warning if called on a guest player.
zh-cn: 当 'player' 关闭 'assetId' 的购买对话框时触发。若玩家已购买该物品，'isPurchased' 为 true，否则为 false。若对访客玩家调用，还会生成一条警告信息。

Source: Returns true if the local device accepts touch input, false otherwise.
en-us: Returns true if the local device accepts touch input, false otherwise.
zh-cn: 若本地设备接受触碰输入则返回 true，否则返回 false。

Source: Returns true if the local device accepts keyboard input, false otherwise.
en-us: Returns true if the local device accepts keyboard input, false otherwise.
zh-cn: 若本地设备接受键盘输入则返回 true，否则返回 false。

Source: Returns true if the local device accepts mouse input, false otherwise.
en-us: Returns true if the local device accepts mouse input, false otherwise.
zh-cn: 若本地设备接受鼠标输入则返回 true，否则返回 false。

Source: Returns true if the local device has an accelerometer, false otherwise.
en-us: Returns true if the local device has an accelerometer, false otherwise.
zh-cn: 若本地设备拥有加速器则返回 true，否则返回 false。

Source: Returns true if the local device has an gyroscope, false otherwise.
en-us: Returns true if the local device has an gyroscope, false otherwise.
zh-cn: 若本地设备拥有陀螺仪则返回 true，否则返回 false。

Source: Fired when a user taps their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the tap gesture. This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user taps their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the tap gesture. This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上轻触手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表轻触手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user pinches their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the pinch gesture. 'scale' is a float that indicates the difference from the beginning of the pinch gesture. 'velocity' is a float indicating how quickly the pinch gesture is happening. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user pinches their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the pinch gesture. 'scale' is a float that indicates the difference from the beginning of the pinch gesture. 'velocity' is a float indicating how quickly the pinch gesture is happening. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上捏合手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表捏合手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。'scale' 是一个浮点数，代表捏合手势距离初始位置的差值。'velocity' 是一个浮点数，代表捏合手势的发生速度。 'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user swipes their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'swipeDirection' is an Enum.SwipeDirection, indicating the direction the user swiped. 'numberOfTouches' is an int that indicates how many touches were involved with the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user swipes their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'swipeDirection' is an Enum.SwipeDirection, indicating the direction the user swiped. 'numberOfTouches' is an int that indicates how many touches were involved with the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上滑动手指时触发。'swipeDirection' 是一个 Enum.SwipeDirection，代表用户滑动的方向。'numberOfTouches' 是一个整数，代表该手势中涉及的触碰数。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user holds at least one finger for a short amount of time on the same screen position on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user holds at least one finger for a short amount of time on the same screen position on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上至少有一根手指在同一屏幕位置上短时间停留时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user rotates two fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'rotation' is a float indicating how much the rotation has gone from the start of the gesture. 'velocity' is a float that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user rotates two fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'rotation' is a float indicating how much the rotation has gone from the start of the gesture. 'velocity' is a float that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上旋转两根手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。 'rotation' 是一个浮点数，代表从手势初始位置所行进的旋转距离。'velocity' 是一个浮点数，代表手势的发生速度。 'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。 此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user drags at least one finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'totalTranslation' is a Vector2, indicating how far the pan gesture has gone from its starting point. 'velocity' is a Vector2 that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed in each dimension. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user drags at least one finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'totalTranslation' is a Vector2, indicating how far the pan gesture has gone from its starting point. 'velocity' is a Vector2 that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed in each dimension. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上拖动至少一根手指时触发。 'totalTranslation' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。 'totalTranslation' 是一个 Vector2，代表平移手势从其初始点所行进的距离。'velocity' 是一个 Vector2，代表手势在各维度上的发生速度。 'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user places their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user places their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户将手指放置在 TouchEnabled 设备上时触发。'touch' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user moves their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user moves their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上移动他们的手指时触发。'touch' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user moves their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user moves their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touch' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上移动他们的手指时触发。'touch' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user begins interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button down, touch begin, keyboard button down, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user begins interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button down, touch begin, keyboard button down, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户开始通过人机交互设备进行交互 (按下鼠标键、触碰开始、按下键盘按键等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user changes interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse move, touch move, mouse wheel, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user changes interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse move, touch move, mouse wheel, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户改变人机交互设备的交互 (鼠标移动、触碰移动、鼠标滚轮等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user stops interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button up, touch end, keyboard button up, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
en-us: Fired when a user stops interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button up, touch end, keyboard button up, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
zh-cn: 当用户停止通过人际交互设备进行交互 (松开鼠标键、触碰结束、松开键盘按键等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个 InputObject，包含查询用户输入的有用数据。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

Source: Fired when a user clicks/taps on a textbox to begin text entry. Argument is the textbox that was put in focus. This also fires if a textbox forces focus on the user. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Fired when a user clicks/taps on a textbox to begin text entry. Argument is the textbox that was put in focus. This also fires if a textbox forces focus on the user. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 当用户单击/轻触文本框开始输入文本时触发。参数为进入焦点的文本框。如果文本框强制成为用户焦点，此事件也会触发。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Fired when a user stops text entry into a textbox (usually by pressing return or clicking/tapping somewhere else on the screen). Argument is the textbox that was taken out of focus. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Fired when a user stops text entry into a textbox (usually by pressing return or clicking/tapping somewhere else on the screen). Argument is the textbox that was taken out of focus. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 当用户停止对文本框进行文本输入 (一般指按下回车或单击/轻触屏幕上的其他位置) 时触发。参数为失去焦点的文本框。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Fired when a user moves a device that has an accelerometer. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Fired when a user moves a device that has an accelerometer. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 当用户移动拥有加速度传感器的设备时触发。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Accelerometer 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的 G 力的位置。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Fired when the force of gravity changes on a device that has an accelerometer. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Fired when the force of gravity changes on a device that has an accelerometer. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 当拥有加速器的设备重力发生改变时触发。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Accelerometer 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的 G 力的位置。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Fired when a user rotates a device that has an gyroscope. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Gyroscope, and position that shows total rotation in each local device axis.  The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. A second argument of Vector4 is the device's current quaternion rotation in reference to it's default reference frame. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Fired when a user rotates a device that has an gyroscope. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Gyroscope, and position that shows total rotation in each local device axis.  The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. A second argument of Vector4 is the device's current quaternion rotation in reference to it's default reference frame. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 当用户旋转拥有陀螺仪的设备时触发。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Gyroscope 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的总旋转量的位置。delta 属性描述最后发生的旋转量。Vector4 的第二个参数为设备相对其默认参考帧的当前四元数旋转值。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Returns an InputObject that describes the device's current acceleration. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis.  The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Returns an InputObject that describes the device's current acceleration. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis.  The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 返回一个描述设备当前加速度的 InputObject。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Accelerometer 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的 G 力的位置。delta 属性描述最后发生的旋转量。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Returns an InputObject that describes the device's current gravity vector. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Returns an InputObject that describes the device's current gravity vector. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Accelerometer, and position that shows the g force in each local device axis. The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 返回一个描述设备当前重力矢量的 InputObject。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Accelerometer 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的 G 力的位置。delta 属性描述最后发生的旋转量。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Returns an InputObject and a Vector4 that describes the device's current rotation vector. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Gyroscope, and position that shows total rotation in each local device axis. The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. The Vector4 is the device's current quaternion rotation in reference to it's default reference frame. This event only fires locally.
en-us: Returns an InputObject and a Vector4 that describes the device's current rotation vector. This is fired with an InputObject, which has type Enum.InputType.Gyroscope, and position that shows total rotation in each local device axis. The delta property describes the amount of rotation that last happened. The Vector4 is the device's current quaternion rotation in reference to it's default reference frame. This event only fires locally.
zh-cn: 返回一个 InputObject 和一个描述设备当前旋转矢量的 Vector4。此触发提供一个包含 Enum.InputType.Gyroscope 类型的 InputObject，以及显示本地设备各轴线上的总旋转量的位置。delta 属性描述最后发生的旋转量。Vector4 是设备的相对其默认参考帧的当前四元数旋转值。此事件仅在本地触发。

Source: Attempts to move the Humanoid and it's associated character to 'part'. 'location' is used as an offset from part's origin.
en-us: Attempts to move the Humanoid and it's associated character to 'part'. 'location' is used as an offset from part's origin.
zh-cn: 尝试使 Humanoid 及其相关角色向 'part' 移动。 'location' 是 part 原始位置的偏移量。

Source: Decreases health by the amount.  Use this instead of changing health directly to make sure weapons are filtered for things such as ForceField(s).
en-us: Decreases health by the amount.  Use this instead of changing health directly to make sure weapons are filtered for things such as ForceField(s).
zh-cn: 减少相应数量的生命值。使用此方法取代直接修改生命值，以确保武器经过 ForceField 等的筛选。

Source: Takes any active gear/tools that the Humanoid is using and puts them into the backpack.  This function only works on Humanoids with a corresponding Player.
en-us: Takes any active gear/tools that the Humanoid is using and puts them into the backpack.  This function only works on Humanoids with a corresponding Player.
zh-cn: 取 Humanoid 正在使用的任意活跃装备/工具并将其放入背包。此函数仅适用于拥有对应 Player 的 Humanoid。

Source: Takes a specified tool and equips it to the Humanoid's Character.  Tool argument should be of type 'Tool'.
en-us: Takes a specified tool and equips it to the Humanoid's Character.  Tool argument should be of type 'Tool'.
zh-cn: 取一件指定工具并将其装备至 Humanoid 的角色。工具参数应为 'Tool' 类型。

Source: Replaces the desired bodypart on the Humanoid's Character using a specified Enum.BodyPartR15 and BasePart. Returns a success boolean.
en-us: Replaces the desired bodypart on the Humanoid's Character using a specified Enum.BodyPartR15 and BasePart. Returns a success boolean.
zh-cn: 用一个指定 Enum.BodyPartR15 和 BasePart 取代 Humanoid 的角色上的身体部件。返回一个成功布尔值。

Source: Returns a Enum.BodyPartR15 given a body part in the Humanoid's Character.
en-us: Returns a Enum.BodyPartR15 given a body part in the Humanoid's Character.
zh-cn: 返回 Humanoid 的 Character 上指定身体部件的 Enum.BodyPartR15。

Source: Sets how to display other humanoid names to this humanoid's player. More info
en-us: Sets how to display other humanoid names to this humanoid's player. More info
zh-cn: 设置如何向此 Humanoid 的玩家显示其他 Humanoid 的名称。更多信息

Source: How many hit points the Humanoid has.  When this number reaches 0 or goes below 0, the Humanoid's character falls apart and will respawn.
en-us: How many hit points the Humanoid has.  When this number reaches 0 or goes below 0, the Humanoid's character falls apart and will respawn.
zh-cn: 此 Humanoid 所拥有的生命值。当此值下降至 0 或以下时，此 Humanoid 的角色会破碎并重生。

Source: The maximum number of hit points a Humanoid's health can reach.  If the Humanoid's health is set over this amount, the health gets set to this value.
en-us: The maximum number of hit points a Humanoid's health can reach.  If the Humanoid's health is set over this amount, the health gets set to this value.
zh-cn: 一个 Humanoid 可以达到的最大生命值。若此 Humanoid 的生命值被设为高于此数值，会自动降低至此数值。

Source: The location that the Humanoid is trying to walk to.
en-us: The location that the Humanoid is trying to walk to.
zh-cn: 此 Humanoid 正尝试走向的位置。

Source: Humanoid.RootPart will be the preferred way of getting a character's humanoid root part.
en-us: Humanoid.RootPart will be the preferred way of getting a character's humanoid root part.
zh-cn: Humanoid.RootPart 是获取角色的 humanoid 根部件的首选方式。

Source: In R6 this property get the player's left leg. In R15 this gets nothing.
en-us: In R6 this property get the player's left leg. In R15 this gets nothing.
zh-cn: 在 R6 中此属性可获取玩家的左腿。在 R15 中无作用。

Source: In R6 this property get the player's right leg. In R15 this gets nothing.
en-us: In R6 this property get the player's right leg. In R15 this gets nothing.
zh-cn: 在 R6 中此属性可获取玩家的右腿。在 R15 中无作用。

Source: An emum that selects the collision type for R15 and Rthro characters. InnerBox is classic style collisions for all characters, OuterBox is dynamically sized collisions based on Mesh size.

Source: Returns a copy of this Object and all its children. The copy's Parent is nil
en-us: Returns a copy of this Object and all its children. The copy's Parent is nil
zh-cn: 请改用 Clone()

Source: Returns a boolean if this Instance is of type 'className' or a is a subclass of type 'className'. If 'className' is not a valid class type in ROBLOX, this function will always return false. More info
en-us: Returns a boolean if this Instance is of type 'className' or a is a subclass of type 'className'. If 'className' is not a valid class type in ROBLOX, this function will always return false. More info
zh-cn: 返回一个布尔值，判断此 Instance 是否为 'className' 类型或 'className' 类型的子类。若 'className' 不是 ROBLOX 中的有效类类型，此函数将始终返回 false。更多信息

Source: Returns the first child of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'name' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first child of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'name' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 请改用 FindFirstChild()

Source: Returns the first child of this Instance that with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first child of this Instance that with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 返回此 Instance 中 ClassName 等于 'className' 的第一个子类。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

Source: Returns the first child of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'className' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first child of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'className' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 返回此 Instance 中符合 IsA(className) 的第一个子类。第二个参数 'recursive' 是一个可选布尔值 (默认为 false)，参数为 true 时将强制此调用遍历此 Instance 的所有后代直到其找到一个名称与 'className' 参数匹配的对象。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

Source: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 返回此 Instance 的匹配第一个参数 'name' 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

Source: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 返回此 Instance 的 ClassName 等于 'className' 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

Source: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
en-us: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
zh-cn: 返回此 Instance 的符合 IsA(className) 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

Source: Returns a string that shows the path from the root node (DataModel) to this Instance.  This string does not include the root node (DataModel).
en-us: Returns a string that shows the path from the root node (DataModel) to this Instance.  This string does not include the root node (DataModel).
zh-cn: 返回一个显示从根节点 (DataModel) 至此 Instance 的路径的字符串。此字符串不包括根节点 (DataModel)。

en-us: Returns a read-only table of this Object's children
zh-cn: 返回一个包含此 Object 的所有子类的只读表

Source: Returns an array containing all of the descendants of the instance. Returns in preorder traversal, or in other words, where the parents come before their children, depth first.
en-us: Returns an array containing all of the descendants of the instance. Returns in preorder traversal, or in other words, where the parents come before their children, depth first.
zh-cn: 返回一个包含此实例的所有后代的数组。返回值为前序遍历，换言之，父类将排在子类的前面，深度优先。

Source: Deprecated. Use ClearAllChildren() to get rid of all child objects, or Destroy() to invalidate this object and its descendants
en-us: Deprecated. Use ClearAllChildren() to get rid of all child objects, or Destroy() to invalidate this object and its descendants
zh-cn: 请改用 Remove()

Source: Removes all children (but not this object) from the workspace.
en-us: Removes all children (but not this object) from the workspace.
zh-cn: 从工作区移除所有子类 (不包括此对象)。

Source: Removes object and all of its children from the workspace. Disconnects object and all children from open connections. Object and children may not be usable after calling Destroy.
en-us: Removes object and all of its children from the workspace. Disconnects object and all children from open connections. Object and children may not be usable after calling Destroy.
zh-cn: 从工作区移除此对象及其所有子类。从开放连接断开此对象及其所有子类。在调用 Destroy 后此对象及其子类可能无法使用。

Source: Fired when any of this object's ancestors change.  First argument 'child' is the object whose parent changed.  Second argument 'parent' is the first argument's new parent.
en-us: Fired when any of this object's ancestors change.  First argument 'child' is the object whose parent changed.  Second argument 'parent' is the first argument's new parent.
zh-cn: 当此对象的任意祖先发生变动时触发。第一个参数 'child' 是父类发生变动的对象。第二个参数 'parent' 是第一个参数的新父类。

Source: Fired after an Instance is parented to this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
en-us: Fired after an Instance is parented to this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
zh-cn: 当一个 Instance 成为此对象或此对象的任意后代的父类时触发。 'descendant' 参数是被添加的 Instance。

Source: Fired after an Instance is unparented from this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
en-us: Fired after an Instance is unparented from this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
zh-cn: 当一个 Instance 与此对象或此对象的任意后代脱离父类关系后触发。 'descendant' 参数是被添加的 Instance。

Source: Fired after a property changes value.  The property argument is the name of the property
en-us: Fired after a property changes value.  The property argument is the name of the property
zh-cn: 当一个属性的值发生变动时触发。属性参数是该属性的名称

Source: A propulsion system that mimics a rocket
en-us: A propulsion system that mimics a rocket
zh-cn: 一种模仿火箭的推进系统

Source: The maximum force that will be exerted on the Part in each axis
en-us: The maximum force that will be exerted on the Part in each axis
zh-cn: 请改用 MaxForce

Source: The amount of power we add to the system.  The higher the power, the quicker the force will achieve its goal.
en-us: The amount of power we add to the system.  The higher the power, the quicker the force will achieve its goal.
zh-cn: 我们添加到系统的功率数值。功率越高，力达成目标的速度就越快。

Source: The velocity this system tries to achieve.  How quickly the system reaches this velocity (if ever) is defined by P.
en-us: The velocity this system tries to achieve.  How quickly the system reaches this velocity (if ever) is defined by P.

en-us: When parented to a physical part, BodyForce will continually exert a force upon its parent object.
zh-cn: 当成为物理部件的子类时，BodyForce 将对其父对象持续施加一个力。

en-us: The power continually applied to this force

en-us: The Vector3 location of where to apply the force to.

Source: This Service-level object is the container for all Team objects in a level. A map that supports team games must have a Teams service. More info
en-us: This Service-level object is the container for all Team objects in a level. A map that supports team games must have a Teams service. More info
zh-cn: 此 Service 级对象是一个关卡中所有 Team 对象的容器。支持组队游戏的地图必须拥有 Team 服务。更多信息

Source: Returns a read-only table of players which are on this team.
en-us: Returns a read-only table of players which are on this team.
zh-cn: 返回一个包含在此队伍中的所有玩家的只读表。

en-us: The Team class is used to represent a faction in a team game. The only valid location for a Team object is under the Teams service. More info
zh-cn: Team 类用于代表组队游戏中的一个阵营。Team 对象的唯一有效位置是在 Teams 服务下。更多信息

Source: The name of the player who is currently editing the script in Team Create.
en-us: The name of the player who is currently editing the script in Team Create.

en-us: A script that runs on clients, NOT servers.  LocalScripts can only run when parented under one of the following:1) A player's Backpack.2) A player's Character model.3) A player's PlayerGui.4) A player's PlayerScripts.5) The ReplicatedFirst service.
zh-cn: 在客户端而非服务器上运行的脚本。LocalScript 只有作为以下类的子类时才能运行: 1) 玩家的背包。2) 玩家的 Character 模型。3) 玩家的 PlayerGui。4) 玩家的 PlayerScripts。5) ReplicatedFirst 服务。

en-us: dummy summary

Source: A construct used to group Parts and other objects together, also allows manipulation of multiple objects.
en-us: A construct used to group Parts and other objects together, also allows manipulation of multiple objects.
zh-cn: 用于将 Part 和其他对象组合在一起的构造，允许对多个对象进行操作。

Source: Breaks all surface joints contained within
en-us: Breaks all surface joints contained within
zh-cn: 断开包含在内的所有表面接头

Source: Returns a CFrame that has position of the centroid of all Parts in the Model.  The rotation matrix is either the rotation matrix of the user-defined PrimaryPart, or if not specified then  a part in the Model chosen by the engine.
en-us: Returns a CFrame that has position of the centroid of all Parts in the Model.  The rotation matrix is either the rotation matrix of the user-defined PrimaryPart, or if not specified then  a part in the Model chosen by the engine.
zh-cn: 返回一个包含 Model 内所有 Part 的质心位置的 CFrame。旋转矩阵可以是用户指定的 PrimaryPart 的旋转矩阵，若用户未指定则由引擎选择 Model 中的一个部件。

Source: Returns a Vector3 that is union of the extents of all Parts in the model.
en-us: Returns a Vector3 that is union of the extents of all Parts in the model.
zh-cn: 返回 Model 中所有 Part 的范围并集 Vector3。

Source: Creates the appropriate SurfaceJoints between all touching Parts contrained within the model. Technically, this function calls MakeJoints() on all Parts inside the model.
en-us: Creates the appropriate SurfaceJoints between all touching Parts contrained within the model. Technically, this function calls MakeJoints() on all Parts inside the model.
zh-cn: 请改用 MakeJoints()

Source: Moves the centroid of the Model to the specified location, respecting all relative distances between parts in the model.
en-us: Moves the centroid of the Model to the specified location, respecting all relative distances between parts in the model.
zh-cn: 将 Model 的质心移至指定位置，保留模型中所有部件之间的相对距离。

Source: Rotates all parts in the model to the orientation that was set using SetIdentityOrientation().  If this function has never been called, rotation is reset to GetModelCFrame()'s rotation.
en-us: Rotates all parts in the model to the orientation that was set using SetIdentityOrientation().  If this function has never been called, rotation is reset to GetModelCFrame()'s rotation.
zh-cn: 将模型中的所有部件旋转至通过 SetIdentityOrientation() 设置的指定朝向。若此函数先前从未被调用，旋转值将重置为 GetModelCFrame() 的旋转值。

Source: Takes the current rotation matrix of the model and stores it as the model's identity matrix. The rotation is applied when ResetOrientationToIdentity() is called.
en-us: Takes the current rotation matrix of the model and stores it as the model's identity matrix. The rotation is applied when ResetOrientationToIdentity() is called.
zh-cn: 取模型的当前旋转矩阵并将其储存为该模型的单位矩阵。调用 ResetOrientationToIdentity() 时应用旋转值。

Source: Similar to MoveTo(), except instead of moving to an explicit location, we use the model's current CFrame location and offset it.
en-us: Similar to MoveTo(), except instead of moving to an explicit location, we use the model's current CFrame location and offset it.
zh-cn: 与 MoveTo() 类似，但不直接移动至明确位置，而是使用模型的当前 CFrame 位置进行偏移。

Source: Returns the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error.
en-us: Returns the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error.
zh-cn: 返回 Model.PrimaryPart 的 CFrame。若 PrimaryPart 为空值，此函数会报错。

Source: Sets the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error. This also sets the cframe of all descendant Parts relative to the cframe change to PrimaryPart.
en-us: Sets the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error. This also sets the cframe of all descendant Parts relative to the cframe change to PrimaryPart.
zh-cn: 设置 Model.PrimaryPart 的 CFrame。若 PrimaryPart 为空值，此函数会报错。还会设置与 PrimaryPart 的 CFrame 改动相关的所有后代 Part 的 CFrame。

Source: Use MoveTo() instead
en-us: Use MoveTo() instead
zh-cn: 请改用 MoveTo()

Source: A Part that serves as a reference for the Model's CFrame. Used in conjunction with GetModelPrimaryPartCFrame and SetModelPrimaryPartCFrame. Use this to rotate/translate all Parts relative to the PrimaryPart.
en-us: A Part that serves as a reference for the Model's CFrame. Used in conjunction with GetModelPrimaryPartCFrame and SetModelPrimaryPartCFrame. Use this to rotate/translate all Parts relative to the PrimaryPart.
zh-cn: 作为 Model 的 CFrame 的参照物的 Part。与 GetModelPrimaryPartCFrame 和 SetModelPrimaryPartCFrame 结合使用。使用此方法旋转/转变与 PrimaryPart 相关的所有 Part。

Source: Use MoveTo() instead

zh-cn: 请改用 MoveTo()

zh-cn: ROBLOX 的父子层次结构的根 (对于用来访问它的全局变量，俗称“游戏”)

Source: Returns true if the game has finished loading, false otherwise.  Check this before listening to the Loaded signal to ensure a script knows when a game finishes loading.
en-us: Returns true if the game has finished loading, false otherwise.  Check this before listening to the Loaded signal to ensure a script knows when a game finishes loading.
zh-cn: 若游戏已加载完毕则返回 true，否则返回 false。在监听 Loaded 信号前先检查此项以确保脚本知道游戏何时完成加载。

Source: Fires when the game finishes loading.  Use this to know when to remove your custom loading gui.  It is best to check IsLoaded() before connecting to this event, as the game may load before the event is connected to.
en-us: Fires when the game finishes loading.  Use this to know when to remove your custom loading gui.  It is best to check IsLoaded() before connecting to this event, as the game may load before the event is connected to.
zh-cn: 当游戏加载完毕时触发。使用此事件来获知何时应移除你的自定义加载界面。最好在连接至此事件前先检查 IsLoaded()，因为游戏可能在事件连接前载入。

Source: Use SetPlaceId() instead
en-us: Use SetPlaceId() instead
zh-cn: 请改用 SetPlaceId()

Source: Use SetCreatorId() instead
en-us: Use SetCreatorId() instead
zh-cn: 请改用 SetCreatorId()

Source: Responsible for storing data across multiple user created places
en-us: Responsible for storing data across multiple user created places
zh-cn: 负责在多个用户创建场景之间储存数据

Source: Returns a data store with the given name and scope
en-us: Returns a data store with the given name and scope
zh-cn: 返回具有指定名称和作用域的数据存储

Source: Returns the default data store
en-us: Returns the default data store
zh-cn: 返回数据存储

Source: Returns an ordered data store with the given name and scope
en-us: Returns an ordered data store with the given name and scope
zh-cn: 返回具有指定名称和作用域的经过排序的数据存储

en-us: Exposes functions for saving and loading data for the DataStoreService
zh-cn: 公开用于为 DataStoreService 保存和加载数据的函数

Source: Sets callback as a function to be executed any time the value associated with key is changed. It is important to disconnect the connection when the subscription to the key is no longer needed.
en-us: Sets callback as a function to be executed any time the value associated with key is changed. It is important to disconnect the connection when the subscription to the key is no longer needed.
zh-cn: 将回调设置为与键关联的值发生改动时执行的函数。不再需要订阅键时断开连接非常重要。

Source: Returns the value of the entry in the DataStore with the given key
en-us: Returns the value of the entry in the DataStore with the given key
zh-cn: 返回 DataStore 中指定键的条目的值

Source: Increments the value of a particular key amd returns the incremented value
en-us: Increments the value of a particular key amd returns the incremented value
zh-cn: 递增指定键的值并返回递增后的值

Source: Sets the value of the key. This overwrites any existing data stored in the key
en-us: Sets the value of the key. This overwrites any existing data stored in the key
zh-cn: 设置键的值。此操作会覆盖键中储存的现有数据

Source: Retrieves the value of the key from the website, and updates it with a new value. The callback until the value fetched matches the value on the web. Returning nil means it will not save.
en-us: Retrieves the value of the key from the website, and updates it with a new value. The callback until the value fetched matches the value on the web. Returning nil means it will not save.
